statements.sql: select count(*) as aggregate from `videos` as `v` left join `users` as `u` on `v`.`user_id` = `u`.`user_id` left join `user_verify` as `uv` on `uv`.`user_id` = `u`.`user_id` left join `sounds` as `s` on `s`.`sound_id` = `v`.`sound_id` left join `likes` as `l` on `l`.`video_id` = `v`.`video_id` and `l`.`user_id` = '5' left join `blocked_users` as `bu1` on `v`.`user_id` = `bu1`.`user_id` and  ( bu1.blocked_by=5 OR bu1.user_id=5 ) left join `blocked_users` as `bu2` on `v`.`user_id` = `bu2`.`blocked_by` and  ( bu2.blocked_by=5 OR bu2.user_id=5 ) left join `follow` as `f2` on `v`.`user_id` = `f2`.`follow_to` and `f2`.`follow_by` = '5' where `v`.`privacy` <> '1' and `v`.`deleted` = 0 and `v`.`enabled` = 1 and `v`.`active` = 1 and `v`.`total_report` < 50 and  bu1.block_id is null and bu2.block_id is null  and  CASE WHEN (f2.follow_id is not null ) THEN (v.privacy=2 OR v.privacy=0) ELSE v.privacy=0 END

select v.video_id,v.sound_id,'http://localhost/default/music-icon.png' as sound_image_url,v.user_id,v.description,v.title,case when u.user_dp!='' THEN case when INSTR(u.user_dp,'https://') > 0 THEN u.user_dp ELSE concat('http://localhost/storage/profile_pic/',v.user_id,'/small/',u.user_dp) END ELSE '' END as user_dp, concat('http://localhost/storage/videos/',v.user_id,'/',video) as video,case when thumb='' then '' else concat('http://localhost/storage/videos/',v.user_id,'/thumb/',thumb) end as thumb,ifnull(case when thumb='' then '' else concat('http://localhost/storage/videos/',v.user_id,'/thumb/',thumb) end,'') as thumb,ifnull(s.title,'') as sound_title,concat('@',u.username) as username,
v.privacy,v.duration,v.user_id,v.tags,ifnull(v.created_at,'NA') as created_at,ifnull(v.updated_at,'NA') as updated_at,
ifnull(l.like_id,0) as like_id,ifnull(f2.follow_id,0) as isFollowing,
(CASE WHEN v.total_likes >= 1000000000
THEN concat(FORMAT(v.total_likes/1000000000,2),' ','B')
WHEN v.total_likes >= 1000000
THEN concat(FORMAT(v.total_likes/1000000,2),' ','M')
WHEN v.total_likes >= 1000
THEN concat(FORMAT(v.total_likes/1000,2),' ','K')
ELSE
v.total_likes
END) as total_likes,
(CASE WHEN v.total_comments >= 1000000000
THEN concat(FORMAT(v.total_comments/1000000000,2),' ','B')
WHEN v.total_comments >= 1000000
THEN concat(FORMAT(v.total_comments/1000000,2),' ','M')
WHEN v.total_comments >= 1000
THEN concat(FORMAT(v.total_comments/1000,2),' ','K')
ELSE
v.total_comments
END) as total_comments,
IF(uv.verified='A', true, false) as isVerified from `videos` as `v` left join `users` as `u` on `v`.`user_id` = `u`.`user_id` left join `user_verify` as `uv` on `uv`.`user_id` = `u`.`user_id` left join `sounds` as `s` on `s`.`sound_id` = `v`.`sound_id` left join `likes` as `l` on `l`.`video_id` = `v`.`video_id` and `l`.`user_id` = '5' left join `blocked_users` as `bu1` on `v`.`user_id` = `bu1`.`user_id` and  ( bu1.blocked_by=5 OR bu1.user_id=5 ) left join `blocked_users` as `bu2` on `v`.`user_id` = `bu2`.`blocked_by` and  ( bu2.blocked_by=5 OR bu2.user_id=5 ) left join `follow` as `f2` on `v`.`user_id` = `f2`.`follow_to` and `f2`.`follow_by` = '5' where `v`.`privacy` <> '1' and `v`.`deleted` = 0 and `v`.`enabled` = 1 and `v`.`active` = 1 and `v`.`total_report` < 50 and  bu1.block_id is null and bu2.block_id is null  and  CASE WHEN (f2.follow_id is not null ) THEN (v.privacy=2 OR v.privacy=0) ELSE v.privacy=0 END  order by RAND() asc limit 10 offset 0
